urs) Formula Setup - Add calculated columns for ROI tracking View Creation - Build filtered views (Active Projects, Revenue Generators, etc.) Button Actions - Create one-click workflows for common tasks Template System - Build reusable content templates Alternative Option: Airtable (More Database-Focused) Airtable Strengths for Your Use Case: Implementation Area\tTactical Steps\tTime Investment\tBusiness Value Content Database\tImport via CSV/markdown, create linked tables\t1-2 hours\tOrganized content library Client Project Tracking\tBuild CRM-style project management\t2-3 hours\tBetter client deliverables Automation Setup\tConnect to Zapier/Make for workflow automation\t1-2 hours\tStreamlined operations Reporting Dashboard\tCreate views for revenue tracking and content performance\t2-3 hours\tData-driven decisions User-Friendly Alternative: AFFiNE (Open Source) AFFiNE Implementation Guide: Advantages: ✅ Free and open-source ✅ Notion-like interface but more responsive ✅ Excellent markdown support ✅ Local-first with cloud sync option ✅ Built-in table creation tools Setup Process: Download from AFFiNE.pro Import Strategy - Bulk import your GenSpark markdown files Table Configuration - Use database blocks for content organization Workflow Setup - Create templates and automation rules Tactical Implementation Roadmap Using Tool | MCP Chart Server MCP: generate_flow_diagram {\"width\":900,\"data\":{\"edges\":[{\"name\":\"Export Content\",\"source\":\"GenSpark Archive\",\"target\":\"Platform Selection\"},{\"name\":\"Choose Coda\",\"source\":\"Platform Selection\",\"target\":\"Coda Setup\"},{\"name\":\"Choose Airtable\",\"source\":\"Platform Selection\",\"target\":\"Airtable Setup\"},{\"name\":\"Choose AFFiNE\",\"source\":\"Platform Selection\",\"target\":\"AFFiNE Setup\"},{\"name\":\"Import Content\",\"source\":\"Coda Setup\",\"target\":\"Content Organization\"},{\"name\":\"Import Data\",\"source\":\"Airtable Setup\",\"target\":\"Content Organization\"},{\"name\":\"Import