th\tUser-friendly with HTML support Notion\t❌ No direct import\t⭐⭐ Limited via embeds\t⭐⭐⭐⭐ Database tables\t⭐⭐⭐⭐ Good search\t$8/month\tGeneral workspace (no HTML import) Coda\t❌ Security blocked\t❌ No HTML rendering\t⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Excellent\t⭐⭐⭐⭐ Good search\t$10/month\tNOT suitable for HTML import Revenue Optimization with HTML-Compatible Platforms Monetization Strategies: Using Tool | MCP Chart Server MCP: generate_radar_chart {\"width\":600,\"data\":[{\"name\":\"Client Deliverables\",\"value\":95,\"group\":\"Confluence\"},{\"name\":\"Content Creation Speed\",\"value\":85,\"group\":\"Confluence\"},{\"name\":\"Professional Appearance\",\"value\":90,\"group\":\"Confluence\"},{\"name\":\"Search Capabilities\",\"value\":95,\"group\":\"Confluence\"},{\"name\":\"Collaboration Features\",\"value\":92,\"group\":\"Confluence\"},{\"name\":\"Cost Efficiency\",\"value\":70,\"group\":\"Confluence\"},{\"name\":\"Client Deliverables\",\"value\":80,\"group\":\"GitHub Pages\"},{\"name\":\"Content Creation Speed\",\"value\":90,\"group\":\"GitHub Pages\"},{\"name\":\"Professional Appearance\",\"value\":85,\"group\":\"GitHub Pages\"},{\"name\":\"Search Capabilities\",\"value\":75,\"group\":\"GitHub Pages\"},{\"name\":\"Collaboration Features\",\"value\":80,\"group\":\"GitHub Pages\"},{\"name\":\"Cost Efficiency\",\"value\":100,\"group\":\"GitHub Pages\"},{\"name\":\"Client Deliverables\",\"value\":85,\"group\":\"GitBook\"},{\"name\":\"Content Creation Speed\",\"value\":80,\"group\":\"GitBook\"},{\"name\":\"Professional Appearance\",\"value\":88,\"group\":\"GitBook\"},{\"name\":\"Search Capabilities\",\"value\":85,\"group\":\"GitBook\"},{\"name\":\"Collaboration Features\",\"value\":85,\"group\":\"GitBook\"},{\"name\":\"Cost Efficiency\",\"value\":80,\"group\":\"GitBook\"}],\"title\":\"Business Value Comparison for HTML-Compatible Platforms\",\"height\":500} View Final Strategic Recommendation Perfect Dual-Platform Setup: TypingMind Team (You already have! ✅) Primar"}]},{"type":"paragraph",